{"tid":2432174,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金燕玲親認再患乳癌 哽咽：唔難受但好驚","createTime":"2021-03-04T06:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T08:44:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d85f9c802b7aed9f1e2cd31f88968db9ee5e2509","tid":2432174,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"近日金燕玲加入YouTube行列，昨日她在新開的「金燕玲 隨心。隨興」上載了第一條短片，片中她表示今年過了一個頗特別的新年，因為與兩年前一樣，在農曆年前發現自己又患癌症：「今次係我做拉筋嘅時候，突然摸到自己嘅左胸摸到一粒嘢，諗咗一晚之後，第二朝一早去問醫生可以點樣做，檢查完之後，要捱到年初五先證實自己有cancer。」她坦言與其將來有機會在別人口中知道此事，所以倒不如由自己親自同大家講，她還說：「之前我嗰個cancer就呼籲大家要做身體檢查同一定要買保險，但係今次唔係透過檢查發現，而係自己摸到，所以對我嚟講，唔知係上天喺度保祐我，無端端畀我自己摸到呢一粒嘢而發現。」金燕玲表示目前已經做了手術：「雖然我係癌症，但係屬於1期B，割咗呢粒嘢之後，我唔需要切除個胸，但係一定要做電療，呢個喺未開刀之前已經知道，但係我覺得自己係好幸運。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210304/YJA7LHJEFVDFRJAD4V6EJVQLSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210304%2FYJA7LHJEFVDFRJAD4V6EJVQLSI%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=78176836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210304%2FYJA7LHJEFVDFRJAD4V6EJVQLSI%2F&h=acae4af3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210304/YJA7LHJEFVDFRJAD4V6EJVQLSI/</a>"},{"pid":"0c0a3fb006480af633051cd1a66c9f24e6fe60d7","tid":2432174,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"連登話保險呃人"},{"pid":"3cbf5e4c44b45a8f92835543e5219734bb0f8c2c","tid":2432174,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487cfe8112f9352cfe90d379c9a11641d1c2712